{"tid":1696204,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"滿意韓國瑜請舉手！高雄官員0反應","createTime":"2019-11-06T04:50:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T06:54:22.000Z","uid":29917,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0033a34f2e12afc084ba2eda505ecdec038d8d1a","tid":1696204,"uid":29917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T04:50:56.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕高雄市長韓國瑜請假參選總統，上週高雄市議會舉行內政部門質詢，市議員高閔琳詢問在場官員「滿意韓國瑜施政滿意度的請舉手」？結果沒有任何一位官員舉手。<br />\n<br />\n高閔琳10月30日質詢時詢問在場官員，「市長韓國瑜的施政滿意度，覺得很滿意的請舉手！」結果在場無一官員舉手。對此，高閔琳驚訝表示「蛤？內政部門每一個局處，都覺得韓市長......滿意度沒人敢舉手？大家都不滿意？」高閔琳接著又說，「那覺得韓市長做得很好請舉手」，而官員仍是毫無反應。<br />\n<br />\n粉專「打馬悍將粉絲團」分享此尷尬影片後，網友紛紛笑稱「市政團隊卡韓黑韓！」、「連韓國瑜市府官員，都對韓國瑜很不滿意」、「又是介於滿意和不滿意之間的答案」、「這太療癒了我可以看無數次」、「沒人滿意？似乎&hellip;&hellip;蠻正常」、「太好笑了啦，這些韓市長團隊，也不知道韓到底做了什麼事吧」、「高議員這就是您的不對了，第一次大家都默認了，為什麼還要逼問第二次呢？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2523979427883356\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2523979427883356&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnX3Kg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=5b13b41e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2523979427883356</a>"},{"pid":"b24344e204ddb7791142e15b775495a2e60c856f","tid":1696204,"uid":271545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T04:58:05.000Z","msg":"沒有 沒有 沒有<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f81af6b56d504b7dc73d5fb76b557c9f96fcb611","tid":1696204,"uid":131522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:01:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e199808a8049f4bc6b64bffd37305c1418229fd5","tid":1696204,"uid":29917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T06:14:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e05bfebf8a5bcae058eab797596857b041a24a9","tid":1696204,"uid":9726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T06:54:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}